{"tid":1724170,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"臺灣音樂人將巡迴演出收入捐俾星火!!!","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:23:43.000Z","uid":63821,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78198a3738b8dda94edfa6c25cdd9d85c33417c0","tid":1724170,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"農村武裝青年<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TUDIvoice/photos/a.156844878282/10157298855803283/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTUDIvoice%2Fphotos%2Fa.156844878282%2F10157298855803283%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=a8f7376d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TUDIvoice/photos/a.156844878282/10157298855803283/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n有感於香港反送中運動的局勢每況愈下，身在台灣的我們除了分享消息與內心支持以外，能做的事情真的不多。這次農武的巡迴專場，我們也一直思考如何能對香港有些實質的協助，討論之後我們決定，將門票總收入與場館拆票後所得，扣除部分樂手費、交通成本、工作人員費用，全數捐給香港的《星火同盟》，作為抗爭中被捕、被囚者及其家屬的法律諮詢、上庭出入護送、緊急醫療資助。同時也希望大家能持續關心香港反送中運動，2020更要努力守住台灣得來不易的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n最後也要感謝買票來看表演的每一個人，做夥打拼！！<br />\n<br />\n農村武裝青年 敬上<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟FB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=defe542d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n=======================================<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳志寧<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zulinwu/photos/a.454412829009/10156854079109010/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzulinwu%2Fphotos%2Fa.454412829009%2F10156854079109010%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=efbdc207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/zulinwu/photos/a.454412829009/10156854079109010/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n《11月演出活動公佈》<br />\n<br />\n身在台灣<br />\n可以自由地說，自由地唱<br />\n是多麽幸福的事。<br />\n<br />\n感謝農村武裝青年提醒我們<br />\n在台灣還可以一起幫忙香港的事<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/Qpa800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FQpa800&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=70950731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/Qpa800</a><br />\n<br />\n11/22我在共生音樂節的小專場演出<br />\n售票連結 <a href=\"https://reurl.cc/0zWVgM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2F0zWVgM&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b538067e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/0zWVgM</a><br />\n<br />\n演出費也將全數捐給 星火同盟 抗爭支援<br />\n作為反送中抗爭過程被捕、被囚者及其家屬的法律諮詢、上庭出入護送、緊急醫療資助等費用。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一起響應，一起聲援香港！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0Cvsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=defe542d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n還有還有～<br />\n請大家告訴大家<br />\n<br />\n#2020/0111<br />\n#政黨票投基進黨<br />\n#總統票投蔡英文<br />\n#守護台灣民主<br />\n#就是撐香港最好的方式<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n快啲去FB多謝佢哋！！！！同埋瘋狂聽佢哋啲歌！！！！<br />\n[url][/url]"},{"pid":"399d692783ca2b1c89b139655871205a9d6e5e1f","tid":1724170,"uid":102365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動"},{"pid":"cfeb9cdd1a89c2fc91c923c5cc9f63e504affcec","tid":1724170,"uid":264077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8958ff87a58353aede26860b6426fd8f81f54c9f","tid":1724170,"uid":293226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\